判入獄。<br />\n<br />\n======"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T03:35:49.000Z","msg":"警世文"},{"pid":"c3bb32b942d61e9e85c87aead7e48dc6526efe52","tid":1495081,"uid":4285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T03:36:38.000Z","msg":"傾閪咩"},{"pid":"8eecfc452a566b467245bb9d8778f4290f645173","tid":1495081,"uid":83732,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T03:38:39.000Z","msg":"對你老母臭閪"},{"pid":"f08cc6a9b64613face6564d54fe632e531808d50","tid":1495081,"uid":269820,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T03:39:43.000Z","msg":"歷史教導我地同你對話係完全浪費時間！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55ba7343b705cca41fa31b98f672e43b562c4920","tid":1495081,"uid":35005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T03:40:39.000Z","msg":"818後不分和勇"},{"pid":"43eecd5ceed6f407112c5cb73785a9cd09a9e1b9","tid":1495081,"uid":142735,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T03:42:31.000Z","msg":"推，溫故知新<br />\n有咁輝煌的歷史，邊個會想同佢對話"},{"pid":"713894376168bd7381e58e23c8d4783cefd0c622","tid":1495081,"uid":215472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T03:43:19.000Z","msg":"真心, 正苦的對話都係假架...."},{"pid":"226c0f4504b9d0a0a80f3eb150704d06cf1144c5","tid":1495081,"uid":1102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T03:43:31.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母"},{"pid":"3c83cefa6d708ab1f255bb66a3c741b799d9d926","tid":1495081,"uid":42487,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T03:45:01.000Z","msg":"人類總要犯同樣的錯誤.jpg"},{"pid":"8dd49228e404a6bccd28bd90c5c3368dd6985c5a","tid":1495081,"uid":279513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T04:21:55.000Z","msg":"打倒淋奠"},{"pid":"8bcd4fae2089230b5a89c1709be6c1e82f1c4689","tid":1495081,"uid":43468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T08:44:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"